OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FA dad has credited voice notes from
OL,8,Fhis young daughters for keeping him in
OL,9,Frehab during treatment for drug and
OL,10,Falcohol addiction.
OL,12,FEli Portnoy, 41, was receiving
OL,13,Ftreatment at Delamere, an addiction
OL,14,Frehabilitation clinic in Cheshire, for
OL,15,Falcohol, marijuana and prescription
OL,16,Fdrug misuse when he considered leaving
OL,17,Fduring a low moment.
