OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FBut, after receiving the heartbreaking
OL,8,Fmessages from two of his children, the
OL,9,Fentrepreneur decided to stay in
OL,10,Ftreatment which ultimately "saved his
OL,11,Flife".
OL,13,FEli was sent the voice notes from his
OL,14,Ftwo daughters, then aged six and nine,
OL,15,Fafter telling medical staff he wanted
OL,16,Fto leave the facility.
