OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FHis youngest daughter said: "I'm
OL,8,Freally proud of you and I just wanted
OL,9,Fyou to know that I love you. I really
OL,10,Fwant you to stay there so that you can
OL,11,Fbe a better daddy and you don't need
OL,12,Fto drink."
OL,14,FHis other daughter added: "I really
OL,15,Fmiss you but we both know this is for
OL,16,Fthe best, and I'm really proud of you
OL,17,Ffor staying there even though it's
OL,18,Freally hard and really tricky. We love
OL,19,Fyou."
