OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FEli said hearing his daughters' voices
OL,8,Fmade him rethink his decision, helping
OL,9,Fhim complete treatment.
OL,11,FThe decision to enter rehab followed a
OL,12,Ffamily intervention in 2023.
OL,14,FEli said one of his sisters told him
OL,15,Fhe needed to seek help or risk dying,
OL,16,Fwhile his brother warned him to stay
OL,17,Faway from his children unless he
OL,18,Faddressed his addiction.
