OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FOver Christmas that year, while his
OL,8,Fwife of 21 years and their four
OL,9,Fchildren travelled to Disney World in
OL,10,FFlorida, Eli checked into Delamere.
OL,12,F"The last thing I wanted at the time
OL,13,Fwas to go to Disney with my kids," he
OL,14,Fsaid. "Addiction makes you selfish,
OL,15,Fand I couldn't face ruining another
OL,16,Ffamily holiday."
OL,18,FEli said his addiction caused him to
OL,19,Fmiss important family events and
OL,20,Fdamaged relationships with his
OL,21,Fchildren.
