OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FOne evening during treatment, he said
OL,8,Fhe nearly left after becoming
OL,9,Foverwhelmed.
OL,11,F"My wife and kids were only 30 minutes
OL,12,Faway. Everyone was talking about
OL,13,Fordering a takeaway and I didn't know
OL,14,Fwhy I was there," he said.
OL,16,FReflecting on his behaviour while
OL,17,Fusing substances, Eli said: "I used to
OL,18,Fget home and think, 'How quickly can I
OL,19,Fget the kids to bed so I can go and
OL,20,Fget high in the garden?'"
