OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,FHe said entering rehab helped him
OL,8,Funderstand the impact his addiction
OL,9,Fhad on his relationship with his
OL,10,Feldest son. "My son is 19, and it took
OL,11,Frehab for me to realise what's missing
OL,12,Fbecause of my addiction," he said.
OL,14,FEli said he first drank alcohol at the
OL,15,Fage of nine and that his substance use
OL,16,Fescalated over time, later involving
OL,17,Fmarijuana and prescription drugs.
