OL,3,C'We want you to stay so you can be a
OL,4,Cbetter daddy': Daughters plea for
OL,5,Crehab dad
OL,7,F"I knew what to take depending on the
OL,8,Fmood," he said. "If I wanted to party,
OL,9,FI'd drink excessively. If I wanted to
OL,10,Fsleep, I'd smoke weed and take pills."
OL,12,FNow approaching two years sober, Eli
OL,13,Fsaid he is focused on rebuilding
OL,14,Frelationships with his family.
OL,16,F"I can't change the past, but I'm
OL,17,Falways working on being the best dad I
OL,18,Fcan be now."
